ps://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtWV0guS.jpg&h=7b0e60e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:16:30.000Z","msg":"呢條撚樣個博士學位買返黎<br />\n<br />\n事實上，湯博士畢業於浸會學院，2010年5月獲得加拿大藍仕橋大學頒授榮譽博士，並在同年獲世界華商投資基金會頒「世界傑出華人獎」。然而於同年10月，藍仕橋大學因為未能通過當地政府審核，被禁止授予商科碩士和博士學位，湯文亮成為最後一屆博士生。湯文亮同屆，同時獲頒藍仕橋大學榮譽博士學位的世界傑出華人獎得主，還有劉德華、永東直巴董事文國柱和一眾政協常委。<br />\n<br />\n湯文亮向本刊指，是藍仕橋大學主動要求給他學位，自己並沒有捐任何款項，又指博士銜頭對他沒有實質幫助。被問到有否接受正規博士教育時，他回答說：「我讀書很水皮，哈哈。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_705263_0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_705263_0&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDOjOHetkdf0TruP2VOJ8R9E%3D&h=62c72b11\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.nextmgz.com%2Fwebarticle%2F2_705263_0&h=676ecf7a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.nextmgz.com/webarticle/2_705263_0</a>"},{"pid":"d3fcf497a7507ee8359f271c02fdcf96fd0e31c8","tid":2145627,"uid":173002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:18:23.000Z","msg":"湯生，請遵守承諾，吞file落肚。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"974d5c813b107d47bc53ff896355ae1e6fa7bb97","tid":2145627,"uid":156121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:18:54.000Z","msg":"吞啦"},{"pid":"dee215407dd393bdfb9aea72321b6217f0f18f52","tid":2145627,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d319e08b1343e33b0c0213c68d0dab4613468cc6","tid":2145627,"uid":117622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T06:50:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你<br />\n知唔知醜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"美國政府已秒殺咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xUYF0gw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxUYF0gw.jpg&h=f166d824&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"be22841cd0721b327d6ba30ff9d60a067